original_title: Zach and Matt Walk to School
overview: Zach and Matt Walk to School is a rough pilot for a potential series on YouTube. It’s an illustrated comedy in the style of stick figure comics. The two main characters, Zach and Matt, are best friends. Zach being the more eccentric one while Matt is a little more level headed and casual. On their walk to school they get into a small argument. But everyone’s perception of the argument gets bigger and bigger until everyone in the school thinks there will be a big fight between them.
tagline: Wait... it HAS to be a wooden spoon?
title: Zach and Matt Walk to School
